                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17930220-51-defend562 t17930220-51-punish292"></join>
               Imprisoned six months in Newgate
            </rs>, and <rs id="t17930220-51-punish293" type="punishmentDescription">
